"title": "7515: anti-semitism",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7515",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A modern term, used to refer to a hatred of Jews or Arabs. Traces of anti-semitism may be discerned in biblical times.</p>\n<h2>The development of anti-semitism</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:8-Exod1:14\">EXO 1:8–1:14</a></strong> <em>Strictly speaking, this hostility towards the Israelites in Egypt after the death of Joseph was not anti-semitism as this word is now understood.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:15-Exod1:16\">EXO 1:15–1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:22\">EXO 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:9\">EXO 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod5:6-Exod5:9\">EXO 5:6–5:9</a></p>\n<h2>Anti-semitism under Persian rule</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:1-Esth3:14\">EST 3:1–3:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:1-Ezra4:8\">EZR 4:1–4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra4:24\">EZR 4:24</a></p>\n<h2>Anti-semitism under Babylonian rule</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:8-Dan3:23\">DAN 3:8–3:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:3-Dan6:14\">DAN 6:3–6:14</a></p>\n<h2>Anti-semitism under Roman rule</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:1-Acts18:2\">ACT 18:1–18:2</a></strong></p>",
